<p><strong>Q1: What is the premise of "The Blue Umbrella" (2005)?</strong></p>
<p><strong>A1:</strong> Based on Ruskin Bond's short story, "The Blue Umbrella" is a film that follows a young girl named Biniya as she tries to find her lost blue umbrella.</p>
<p><strong>Q2: Who wrote the screenplay for "The Blue Umbrella"?</strong></p>
<p><strong>A2:</strong> The screenplay was written by Ranjit Kapoor, based on Bond's short story.</p>
