<p><strong>Q4: What is the significance of the blue umbrella in the film?</strong></p>
<p><strong>A4:</strong> The blue umbrella symbolizes Biniya's determination and hope. It represents her connection to the outside world and her desire to overcome the challenges she faces.</p>
<p><strong>Q5: What message or theme does "The Blue Umbrella" convey?</strong></p>
<p><strong>A5:</strong> The film explores themes of resilience, hope, and the power of connections. It teaches the importance of perseverance in the face of adversity and the value of kindness and compassion.</p>